      "question_type": "multiple_choice_question",
      "question_text": "<p>A developer moves their <code>&lt;script defer src=\"app.js\"&gt;</code> from the bottom of <code>&lt;body&gt;</code> to <code>&lt;head&gt;</code>. What is the benefit?</p>",
      "points_possible": 1,
      "answers": [
        {
          "id": "defer-benefit_a1",
